<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20181230/98661c875a3848519bb4e73a415cd46f.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">老子道德经：本质原理的形式逻辑</span></img></p>
